{"id":141,"date":"2026-03-31T06:17:27","date_gmt":"2026-03-31T06:17:27","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/how-2.codes\/?p=141"},"modified":"2026-03-31T06:17:27","modified_gmt":"2026-03-31T06:17:27","slug":"how-to-see-your-current-publishing-settings-4-blog-in-microsoft-word","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/how-2.codes\/how-to-see-your-current-publishing-settings-4-blog-in-microsoft-word\/","title":{"rendered":"How to See Your Current Publishing Settings 4 Blog in Microsoft Word"},"content":{"rendered":"<p style=\"margin-left: 144pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">i have word set up to publish directly to my blog but i cant figutre out how to show in the menu which site i can post to i dont want to randomly post how do i see the settings ..&#8221;publishing settings currently set up&#8221;?<span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><br \/>\n\t\t\t<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 36pt\">\u00a0<br \/>\n\u00a0<\/p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 36pt\">\u00a0<br \/>\n\u00a0<\/p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 36pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">To see which blog site you are currently set up to post to in Microsoft Word, you need to use the <strong>Manage Accounts<\/strong> feature within the specialized <strong>Blog Post<\/strong> tab. This tab only appears when you are using the specific blog template. [<a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=VK7tMamWJvA\">1<\/a>, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.lifewire.com\/write-post-blog-using-microsoft-office-2511856\">2<\/a>, <a href=\"https:\/\/learn.microsoft.com\/en-us\/answers\/questions\/5034084\/trying-to-locate-the-blog-post-tab-in-blog-post-te\">3<\/a>]<span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><br \/>\n\t\t\t<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 36pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:15pt\">How to See Your Current Publishing Settings<br \/>\n<\/span><\/p>\n<ul style=\"margin-left: 72pt\">\n<li><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"><strong>Open the Blog Post Template<\/strong>: Go to <strong>File<\/strong> &gt; <strong>New<\/strong> and select <strong>Blog post<\/strong>. This will open a new window with a different set of tabs at the top.<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Roboto; font-size:12pt\"><br \/>\n\t\t\t<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"><strong>Locate the Blog Post Tab<\/strong>: Look at the ribbon (the menu at the top); you should see a unique tab labeled <strong>Blog Post<\/strong>.<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Roboto\"><br \/>\n\t\t\t<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"><strong>Check Your Accounts<\/strong>: In the <strong>Blog<\/strong> group (usually on the far left of that tab), click the <strong>Manage Accounts<\/strong> button.<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Roboto\"><br \/>\n\t\t\t<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"><strong>Review the List<\/strong>: A dialog box will appear listing all the blog accounts you have registered. The account with a checkmark next to it is your <strong>default<\/strong> site\u2014this is where Word will post unless you change it. [<a href=\"https:\/\/support.microsoft.com\/en-us\/office\/help-with-blogging-in-word-3ad4ad8d-06a3-441d-99cd-c65e13a3433d\">1<\/a>, <a href=\"https:\/\/support.microsoft.com\/en-us\/office\/help-with-blogging-in-word-3ad4ad8d-06a3-441d-99cd-c65e13a3433d\">2<\/a>, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=-_D3rnsyoUw\">3<\/a>, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=VK7tMamWJvA\">4<\/a>, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.lifewire.com\/write-post-blog-using-microsoft-office-2511856\">5<\/a>]<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Roboto\"><br \/>\n\t\t\t<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:15pt\">Managing Multiple Sites<br \/>\n<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 36pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">If you have more than one site and want to ensure you aren&#8217;t &#8220;randomly posting,&#8221; you can use the same <strong>Manage Accounts<\/strong> window to: [<a href=\"https:\/\/www.lifewire.com\/write-post-blog-using-microsoft-office-2511856\">1<\/a>]<span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><br \/>\n\t\t\t<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<ul style=\"margin-left: 72pt\">\n<li><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"><strong>Set a New Default<\/strong>: Select the site you want to use and click <strong>Set as Default<\/strong>.<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Roboto; font-size:11pt\"><br \/>\n\t\t\t<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"><strong>Remove Old Sites<\/strong>: Select any accounts you no longer use and click <strong>Remove<\/strong>.<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Roboto; font-size:11pt\"><br \/>\n\t\t\t<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"><strong>Add New Sites<\/strong>: Click <strong>New<\/strong> to register a different blog provider (like WordPress or Blogger). [<a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=-_D3rnsyoUw\">1<\/a>, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.lifewire.com\/write-post-blog-using-microsoft-office-2511856\">3<\/a>, <a href=\"https:\/\/learn.microsoft.com\/en-us\/answers\/questions\/5050461\/setting-default-printer-settings-in-microsoft-word\">4<\/a>, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=QBOSE4YhcQg\">5<\/a>]<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Roboto; font-size:11pt\"><br \/>\n\t\t\t<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">Would you like help <strong>linking a new blog<\/strong> or <strong>setting up a specific platform<\/strong> like WordPress?<span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><br \/>\n\t\t\t<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 36pt\">\u00a0<br \/>\n\u00a0<\/p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 36pt\">\u00a0<br \/>\n\u00a0<\/p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 36pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:10pt\">Show all<br \/>\n<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 360pt\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/how-2.codes\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/03\/033126_0617_HowtoSeeYou1.png\" alt=\"\"\/><span style=\"font-family:Roboto; font-size:11pt\"><br \/>\n\t\t<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 36pt\">\u00a0<br \/>\n\u00a0<\/p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 36pt\">\u00a0<br \/>\n\u00a0<\/p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 36pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">To see which blog site you are currently set up to post to, you can use the <strong>Manage Accounts<\/strong> button located directly in the <strong>Blog Post<\/strong> ribbon of your Word document.<span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><br \/>\n\t\t\t<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 36pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">Based on your image, here is exactly where to look:<br \/>\n<\/span><\/p>\n<ul style=\"margin-left: 72pt\">\n<li><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"><strong>Locate the &#8220;Blog&#8221; Group<\/strong>: On the far left of the <strong>Blog Post<\/strong> tab, there is a section labeled &#8220;Blog&#8221;.<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Roboto; font-size:11pt\"><br \/>\n\t\t\t<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"><strong>Access Your Settings<\/strong>: Click on the <strong>Manage Accounts<\/strong> icon (the one with the small gears and a person).<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Roboto; font-size:11pt\"><br \/>\n\t\t\t<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"><strong>Verify the Active Site<\/strong>: A window will open showing all registered blog accounts. The site with a <strong>checkmark<\/strong> next to it is the one currently active for publishing. [<a href=\"http:\/\/www.dontpapanic.com\/blog\/\">1<\/a>, <a href=\"https:\/\/support.microsoft.com\/en-us\/office\/help-with-blogging-in-word-3ad4ad8d-06a3-441d-99cd-c65e13a3433d\">2<\/a>, <a href=\"https:\/\/learn.microsoft.com\/en-us\/answers\/questions\/5139568\/words-online-missing-right-click-context-menu\">3<\/a>]<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Roboto; font-size:11pt\"><br \/>\n\t\t\t<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">If you want to ensure you aren&#8217;t &#8220;randomly posting,&#8221; you can use that same &#8220;Manage Accounts&#8221; window to <strong>Set as Default<\/strong> the specific site you want or <strong>Remove<\/strong> any old sites you no longer use.<span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><br \/>\n\t\t\t<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 36pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">Do you have multiple accounts listed there, or are you trying to <strong>add a second blog<\/strong> for the first time?<br \/>\n<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 36pt\">\u00a0<br \/>\n\u00a0<\/p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 36pt\">\u00a0<br \/>\n\u00a0<\/p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 36pt\">\u00a0<br \/>\n\u00a0<\/p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 36pt\">\u00a0<br \/>\n\u00a0<\/p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 36pt\">\u00a0<br \/>\n\u00a0<\/p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 36pt\">\u00a0<br \/>\n\u00a0<\/p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 36pt\">\u00a0<br \/>\n\u00a0<\/p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 36pt\">\u00a0<br \/>\n\u00a0<\/p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 36pt\">\u00a0<br \/>\n\u00a0<\/p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 36pt\">\u00a0<br \/>\n\u00a0<\/p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 36pt\">\u00a0<br \/>\n\u00a0<\/p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 36pt\">\u00a0<br \/>\n\u00a0<\/p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 36pt\">\u00a0<br \/>\n\u00a0<\/p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 36pt\">\u00a0<br \/>\n\u00a0<\/p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 36pt\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/how-2.codes\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/03\/033126_0617_HowtoSeeYou2.png\" alt=\"\"\/><span style=\"font-family:Roboto; font-size:11pt\"><br \/>\n\t\t<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 36pt\">\u00a0<br \/>\n\u00a0<\/p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 36pt\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/how-2.codes\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/03\/033126_0617_HowtoSeeYou3.png\" alt=\"\"\/><span style=\"font-family:Roboto; font-size:11pt\"><br \/>\n\t\t<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 36pt\">\u00a0<br \/>\n\u00a0<\/p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 36pt\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/how-2.codes\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/03\/033126_0617_HowtoSeeYou4.png\" alt=\"\"\/><span style=\"font-family:Roboto; font-size:11pt\"><br \/>\n\t\t<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 36pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:10pt\">3 sites<br \/>\n<\/span><\/p>\n<ul style=\"margin-left: 72pt\">\n<li><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">What Me Pa..Panic? \u2013 A BLOG about SharePoint &amp; O365 &#8230;<br \/><\/span><span style=\"font-size:9pt\">A common question that I&#8217;ve run into again lately is how can I set the Selected or Selected Text property of a dropdown control in&#8230;<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:Roboto; font-size:11pt\"><br \/>\n\t\t\t<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/how-2.codes\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/03\/033126_0617_HowtoSeeYou5.png\" alt=\"\"\/><span style=\"font-family:Roboto; font-size:11pt\"><br \/>\n\t\t<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 36pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:9pt\">Don&#8217;t Pa..Panic Consulting<br \/>\n<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 36pt\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/how-2.codes\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/03\/033126_0617_HowtoSeeYou6.png\" alt=\"\"\/><span style=\"font-family:Roboto; font-size:11pt\"><br \/>\n\t\t<\/span><\/p>\n<ul style=\"margin-left: 72pt\">\n<li><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">Help with blogging in Word &#8211; Microsoft Support<br \/><\/span><span style=\"font-size:9pt\">When the Insert tab is selected, you can add photos, hyperlinks, and other items to your post. * Type a title for your post at the&#8230;<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:Roboto; font-size:11pt\"><br \/>\n\t\t\t<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/how-2.codes\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/03\/033126_0617_HowtoSeeYou7.png\" alt=\"\"\/><span style=\"font-family:Roboto; font-size:11pt\"><br \/>\n\t\t<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 36pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:9pt\">Microsoft Support<br \/>\n<\/span><\/p>\n<ul style=\"margin-left: 72pt\">\n<li><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">Words Online Missing Right-Click Context Menu &#8211; Microsoft Q&amp;A<br \/><\/span><span style=\"font-size:9pt\">Aug 14, 2021 \u2014 3 answers \u00b7 Doug Robbins &#8211; MVP &#8211; Office Apps and Services \u2022. Follow. 322.7K Reputation points \u2022 MVP \u2022 Volunteer Moderator \u00b7 Anonym&#8230;<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:Roboto; font-size:11pt\"><br \/>\n\t\t\t<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/how-2.codes\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/03\/033126_0617_HowtoSeeYou8.png\" alt=\"\"\/><span style=\"font-family:Roboto; font-size:11pt\"><br \/>\n\t\t<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 36pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:9pt\">Microsoft Learn<br \/>\n<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 36pt\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/how-2.codes\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/03\/033126_0617_HowtoSeeYou9.png\" alt=\"\"\/><span style=\"font-family:Roboto; font-size:11pt\"><br \/>\n\t\t<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 333pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">hmm an account is missing?<span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><br \/>\n\t\t\t<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 36pt\">\u00a0<br \/>\n\u00a0<\/p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 36pt\">\u00a0<br \/>\n\u00a0<\/p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 36pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">If an account isn&#8217;t appearing in the &#8220;Manage Accounts&#8221; list, it likely hasn&#8217;t been registered in Word on this specific computer yet. Word stores these blog connections locally, so if you&#8217;ve recently updated your software or are using a different device, you&#8217;ll need to re-link it. [<a href=\"https:\/\/support.microsoft.com\/en-us\/office\/help-with-blogging-in-word-3ad4ad8d-06a3-441d-99cd-c65e13a3433d\">1<\/a>, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.bluehost.com\/in\/blog\/a-step-by-step-guide-to-posting-on-wordpress-via-microsoft-word\/\">2<\/a>]<span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><br \/>\n\t\t\t<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 36pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"><strong>How to Add the Missing Account<\/strong><br \/>\n\t\t<\/span><\/p>\n<ul style=\"margin-left: 72pt\">\n<li><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"><strong>Open the Account Manager<\/strong>: From the <strong>Blog Post<\/strong> tab (which you already have open in your screenshot), click <strong>Manage Accounts<\/strong>.<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Roboto\"><br \/>\n\t\t\t<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"><strong>Start a New Registration<\/strong>: Click the <strong>New<\/strong> button at the top of the dialog box.<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Roboto\"><br \/>\n\t\t\t<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"><strong>Select Your Provider<\/strong>: Choose your blog service (e.g., WordPress, Blogger, SharePoint) from the dropdown list. If yours isn&#8217;t listed, choose <strong>Other<\/strong>.<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Roboto\"><br \/>\n\t\t\t<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"><strong>Enter Your Credentials<\/strong>:<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Roboto\"><br \/>\n\t\t\t<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"><strong>Blog URL<\/strong>: Enter the web address of your blog.<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Roboto; font-size:11pt\"><br \/>\n\t\t\t<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"><strong>Username &amp; Password<\/strong>: Use the exact login info you use to sign in to your blog&#8217;s dashboard online.<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Roboto; font-size:11pt\"><br \/>\n\t\t\t<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"><strong>Finalize<\/strong>: Click <strong>OK<\/strong>. Word will attempt to connect to your site. Once successful, it will appear in your account list. [<a href=\"https:\/\/support.microsoft.com\/en-us\/office\/help-with-blogging-in-word-3ad4ad8d-06a3-441d-99cd-c65e13a3433d\">1<\/a>, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.pcworld.com\/article\/435084\/how-to-start-blogging-with-microsoft-word.html\">2<\/a>, <a href=\"https:\/\/sharepointmike.wordpress.com\/2013\/08\/10\/using-microsoft-word-to-write-your-blogs\/\">3<\/a>, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.bluehost.com\/in\/blog\/a-step-by-step-guide-to-posting-on-wordpress-via-microsoft-word\/\">4<\/a>, <a href=\"https:\/\/support.microsoft.com\/en-us\/office\/help-with-blogging-in-word-3ad4ad8d-06a3-441d-99cd-c65e13a3433d\">5<\/a>]<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Roboto; font-size:12pt\"><br \/>\n\t\t\t<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"><strong>Common Reasons for &#8220;Missing&#8221; Accounts<\/strong><br \/>\n\t\t<\/span><\/p>\n<ul style=\"margin-left: 72pt\">\n<li><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"><strong>Device Change<\/strong>: Blog settings do not always sync across different computers, even if you&#8217;re signed into the same Microsoft account.<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Roboto; font-size:11pt\"><br \/>\n\t\t\t<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"><strong>Password Update<\/strong>: If you recently changed your blog password online, Word may &#8220;lose&#8221; the connection until you re-enter the new credentials.<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Roboto; font-size:11pt\"><br \/>\n\t\t\t<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"><strong>Permissions<\/strong>: Ensure you have <strong>Admin<\/strong> or <strong>Editor<\/strong> privileges on the blog site itself, or Word may be unable to verify the account. [<a href=\"https:\/\/support.microsoft.com\/en-us\/office\/help-with-blogging-in-word-3ad4ad8d-06a3-441d-99cd-c65e13a3433d\">1<\/a>, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.bluehost.com\/in\/blog\/a-step-by-step-guide-to-posting-on-wordpress-via-microsoft-word\/\">2<\/a>, <a href=\"https:\/\/support.google.com\/blogger\/thread\/288188287\/can-t-find-my-blog-posts?hl=en\">3<\/a>]<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Roboto; font-size:11pt\"><br \/>\n\t\t\t<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"><strong>Which blog provider<\/strong> (like WordPress or Blogger) are you trying to add back in? I can give you the specific URL format you&#8217;ll need for it.<span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><br \/>\n\t\t\t<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>i have word set up to publish directly to my blog but i cant figutre out how to show in the menu which site i can post to i dont want to randomly post how do i see the settings ..&#8221;publishing settings currently set up&#8221;? \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 To see which blog site you [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_import_markdown_pro_load_document_selector":0,"_import_markdown_pro_submit_text_textarea":"","footnotes":""},"categories":[1],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-141","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","hentry","category-uncategorized"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/how-2.codes\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/141","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/how-2.codes\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/how-2.codes\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/how-2.codes\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/how-2.codes\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=141"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/how-2.codes\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/141\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":142,"href":"https:\/\/how-2.codes\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/141\/revisions\/142"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/how-2.codes\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=141"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/how-2.codes\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=141"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/how-2.codes\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=141"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}